triggers {
  name: "Map-Startup"
  events {
    ops {
      functionName: "On Map Start"
    }
  }
  conditions {
  }
  actions {
    ops {
      functionName: "Set Variable (int)"
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Story Variable (int)"
          args {
            string_value: "51f15c62336331d02c00440e"
          }
          args {
            string_value: "TestDifficulty"
          }
        }
      }
      args {
        int_value: 6
      }
    }
    ops {
      functionName: "Set Variable (int)"
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Story Variable (int)"
          args {
            string_value: "51f169b733633124330018bf"
          }
          args {
            string_value: "Universal_Random"
          }
        }
      }
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Random (int)"
          args {
            int_value: 1
          }
          args {
            int_value: 2
          }
        }
      }
    }
    ops {
      functionName: "Play Music"
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Map Item (Music)"
          args {
            string_value: "Seattle_Set3"
          }
          args {
            string_value: "Seattle-Set3-Combat"
          }
        }
      }
      args {
        float_value: 1
      }
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Preset Value (int)"
          args {
            string_value: "bool"
          }
          args {
            int_value: 1
          }
        }
      }
    }
    ops {
      functionName: "Send Event"
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Map Item (Event)"
          args {
            string_value: "Test"
          }
        }
      }
    }
    ops {
      functionName: "Enable/Disable Manual Turn Mode"
      args {
        call_value {
          functionName: "Get Preset Value (int)"
          args {
            string_value: "EnableOrDisable"
          }
          args {
            int_value: 0
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
  isActive: true
  idRef {
    id: "51f3f89d336331b43900196a"
  }
